service-0'], 'aiops-k8s-05': ['paymentservice-1', 'cartservice-1', 'checkoutservice-2'], 'aiops-k8s-06': ['productcatalogservice-1', 'emailservice-2', 'frontend-1'], 'aiops-k8s-07': ['shippingservice-1', 'emailservice-0', 'currencyservice-1', 'cartservice-0', 'adservice-1'], 'aiops-k8s-08': ['currencyservice-2', 'recommendationservice-0', 'paymentservice-0', 'frontend-2', 'checkoutservice-1', 'productcatalogservice-0', 'cartservice-2', 'adservice-2', 'redis-cart-0']}\n\n\n[ANALYSIS STATE]\n\nCurrent Hypothesis: None\n\nCurrent Iteration: 2\n\n\n[AGENT FINDINGS HISTORY]\n\n--- Log Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的日志数据，我现在进行分析。从日志中可以看到frontend服务在故障时间段内出现了大量的连接错误。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"Unavailable\", \"transport is closing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"端口连接被拒绝错误，frontend服务无法连接到目标服务（IP地址10.233.61.165:5050）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.61.165:5050: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点：**\n\n1. **错误模式识别**：所有错误日志都显示frontend服务在调用购物车结算接口时遇到连接问题\n2. **关键错误信息**：\n   - `connection refused` - 连接被拒绝，表明目标服务端口不可达\n   - `transport: Error while dialing` - 传输层连接错误\n   - `Unavailable` - 服务不可用状态\n   - `transport is closing` - 传输通道关闭\n\n3. **故障分析**：\n   - 报错服务：frontend（调用方）\n   - 被抱怨服务：通过IP地址10.233.61.165:5050推断可能是checkoutservice\n   - 错误类型：端口连接被拒绝，可能是目标服务宕机或端口配置错误\n\n4. **故障特征**：多个frontend实例（frontend-1和frontend-2）在多个节点上同时出现相同错误，表明这是一个系统性的连接问题。\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的指标数据，我已经成功分析了故障时间段。现在让我进行详细分析：\n\n## 分析结果\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"io_util\", \"memory_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务出现严重错误率异常，error_ratio从0.0上升到0.32（变化率2.0），server_error_ratio同样异常，同时rrt_max从252958降至123844.5（下降48.5%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0→0.32 (↑200%), server_error_ratio: 0.0→0.32 (↑200%), rrt_max: 252958→123844.5 (↓51.5%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\", \n      \"reason\": \"前端服务错误率异常，error_ratio从0.0上升到0.31（变化率2.0），server_error_ratio同样异常，rrt_max从250893降至118099.5（下降52.9%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 0.0→0.31 (↑200%), server_error_ratio: 0.0→0.31 (↑200%), rrt_max: 250893→118099.5 (↓52.9%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"货币服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从4842上升到4861，p99变化率高达1.1426，显示尾部延迟显著恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 4842→4861 (↑0.4%), p99变化率: 1.1426 (↑114.26%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"物流服务响应时间异常，rrt_max从1725上升到6027（变化率1.1099），显示严重性能退化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 1725→6027 (↑249.4%), 变化率: 1.1099\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB存储组件IO使用率异常，p99的io_util从0.06上升到0.14（变化率0.8），可能存在存储性能瓶颈\",\n      \"evidence\": \"io_util p99: 0.06→0.14 (↑133.3%), p99变化率: 0.8\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现\n\n**主要故障模式**：\n1. **前端服务错误率激增**：frontend-1和frontend-2的错误率从0%上升到30%以上，这是最显著的异常\n2. **响应时间异常**：多个服务的rrt_max指标出现异常变化，特别是shippingservice-2的响应时间增加了249%\n3. **数据库IO压力**：tidb-tikv的IO使用率p99值显著上升，可能存在存储层瓶颈\n\n**根因分析**：前端服务的错误率异常是最突出的问题，可能由后端服务（如currencyservice、shippingservice）的性能退化引发，而数据库层的IO压力可能是根本原因之一。\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于获取到的trace数据分析，我发现了一个明显的故障模式。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\", \"rrt_max\", \"cartservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从状态码统计可见，checkoutservice出现大量'connection refused'错误（状态码14），frontend调用checkoutservice时出现101次连接拒绝错误，导致HTTP 500错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice调用redis的HGET操作延迟从正常1.74ms激增至7.95ms，延迟倍数达4.57倍，表明redis存在性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用cartservice的GetCart操作延迟从正常2.55ms增至9.72ms，延迟倍数3.8倍，可能是受redis延迟影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n\n1. **主要根因**：checkoutservice服务完全不可用，出现大量\"connection refused\"错误，这是最严重的故障点。\n\n2. **次要问题**：redis服务存在性能瓶颈，HGET操作延迟显著增加，影响cartservice的正常运行。\n\n3. **影响范围**：故障导致frontend服务大量HTTP 500错误，影响用户下单流程。\n\n根据系统拓扑，checkoutservice是核心服务，依赖多个下游服务（Cart、ProductCatalog、Shipping、Payment等），其故障会直接影响整个电商系统的下单功能。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED\n================================\n请基于上述全量信息以及你的 Trace 数据，对当前故障进行分析。\n重点：请在返回 JSON 的 'stance' 字段中明确标记 'SUPPORT', 'OPPOSE' 或 'NEUTRAL'。", "raw_trace_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载trace数据。UUID: a7ed866b-406，共 11 个异常组合，5 个状态组合", "filtered_traces": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,normal_avg_duration,anomaly_avg_duration,anomaly_count\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,153703.35266395428,256.9666666666667,出现次数:35\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder,156733.32721158856,277.75925925925924,出现次数:27\naiops-k8s-07,redis,cartservice-0,cartservice-0,HGET,1739.7426895431556,7952.380847953216,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CartService/GetCart,3932.5934219641285,11290.029411764706,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-07,cartservice,frontend-1,cartservice-0,POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart,2554.211789705742,9722.762808349147,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-03,recommendationservice,recommendationservice-1,recommendationservice-1,/hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/ListProducts,2920.2195046731545,3699.9111842105262,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-06,fronte